{"tid":1389180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到呢一刻，我依然唔支持大家當「鄉=黑」","createTime":"2019-07-31T00:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:45:00.000Z","uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6700d4585b3da1ea20c9f96949a18af61b0c783","tid":1389180,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:08:02.000Z","msg":"因為咁做係團結緊對手<br />\n721無差別攻擊引起民憤 <br />\n原因其中之一就係好多唔關事既人都搞<br />\n咁我想問 <br />\n南邊圍係咪個個都有份收錢打人？<br />\n係咪一個黃絲自己人都無？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過 <span style=\"color: red;\">村長絕對唔係無辜</span><br />\n條友肯定知情同支持所有行動<br />\n如果佢有咩事我唔會同情佢<br />\n另外如果搵到有當日既白衫 大家做乜都得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係唔好無差別咁報復</span>"},{"pid":"b28940de40ae9b2f3d4408885f8cdedddd1eb02b","tid":1389180,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84a1c451df0f2b72443b69cf97c3991560764cc4","tid":1389180,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:11:39.000Z","msg":"負皮既講兩句<br />\n嬲唔係理由 唔好做錯事"},{"pid":"65755fd4cb46007c36b181f3c2a598c615afd3dc","tid":1389180,"uid":6030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:12:26.000Z","msg":"所以叫鄉黑"},{"pid":"495622955baf290e20d15a4f78a582944983d6aa","tid":1389180,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:16:31.000Z","msg":"有份打人者，私刑處決<br />\n法律治唔到就需要私刑"},{"pid":"536e21773b33b162af88d55d56a34edbef130e34","tid":1389180,"uid":288393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84a1c451df0f2b72443b69cf97c3991560764cc4","tid":1389180,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:11:39.000Z","msg":"負皮既講兩句<br />\n嬲唔係理由 唔好做錯事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:16:33.000Z","msg":"叫嗰啲所謂自己人放村入面班鄉黑嘅料上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />囉"},{"pid":"082b8e4361ae8be6b65057b7a4b302781ec30274","tid":1389180,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201